Webex App | Automatically start your video when you join a meeting
If you always turn on your video during a meeting, save yourself the step of having to start it each time.
1
Tap your profile picture and tap Settings > Meetings.
2
Tap Use my default join options.
3
Tap to toggle on Start my video when I join.
Your video turns on automatically each time you join a meeting.
If you change your mind during a meeting, turn off your video.